<%- include("./partials/head.ejs") %>

  <div class="home-page">
    <h2 class="home-title">Bring Back the Snack Wrap</h2>
    <div class="home-container">
      <div class="home-left">
        <div><img class="home-img" src="./sw.jpg" alt=""></div>
        <div class="author">
          <p class="author-title">Petition created by: David Son</p>
          <ul class="author-socials">
            <li><i class="fa-brands fa-github fa-2xl"></i></li>
            <li><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin-in fa-2xl"></i></li>
            <li><i class="fa-solid fa-blog fa-xl"></i></li>
            <li><i class="fa-solid fa-share-from-square fa-xl"></i></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="message">
          <p>
            Many people could agree that McDonald's snack wraps were one of the best items on the menu 
            (personally, McDonald's snack wraps were the second best item in the menu, 
            just barely losing to the fries). Not only were the snack wraps incredibly delicious, 
            they were also relatively healthy.
          </p>
          <p>
            The snack wrap was discontinued in most U.S. locations back in 2016 and removed nation
            wide back in 2020. However, I believe that with enough noise and support, McDonald's
            just might bring them back.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="petition-msg-board">
          <% for(let i = 0; i < petitions.length; i++) { %>
            <div class="petition-msg">
              <div class="petition-msg-left">
                <img src="" alt="profile-pic">
              </div>
              <div class="petition-msg-right">
                <div class="petition-msg-right-top">
                  <span><%= petitions[i].firstName %> <%= petitions[i].lastName %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="petition-msg-right-bot">
                  <p><%= petitions[i].message %></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="home-right">
        <div class="petition-stats">
          <span class="bold">10,000 have signed.</span>
          <span>Let's get 20,000!</span>
          <p>SOMEONE has signed this petition!</p>
          <p>SOMEONE has signed this petition!</p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="petition-signup-title">Sign this petition</h2>
        <form id="petition-signup" action="/signed-petition" method="POST">
          <p>First Name</p>
          <input class="petition-input" type="text" name="firstName">
          <p>Last Name</p>
          <input class="petition-input" type="text" name="lastName">
          <p>Email</p>
          <input class="petition-input" type="email" name="email">
          <p>Message</p>
          <textarea class="petition-input-textarea" name="message" cols="30" rows="5"></textarea>
          <div class="petition-auth-container">
            <input type="checkbox" name="auth-petition">
            <span class="auth-span">Authorize my name and message to be displayed</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <input id="petition-signup-btn" class="btn" type="submit" value="Sign Petition">
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>


<%- include("./partials/footer.ejs") %>